  "prompt": "Is there any Indian celebrity and foreign celebrity who looks similar?",
  "response": "There are several instances where Indian celebrities have been noted to resemble foreign celebrities. Here are a few examples:\n\n1. **Deepika Padukone and Amanda Cerny**:\n   - Indian actress Deepika Padukone is often said to resemble American model and internet personality Amanda Cerny. Both have similar facial structures and smiles.\n\n2. **Aishwarya Rai Bachchan and Anne Hathaway**:\n   - Bollywood star Aishwarya Rai Bachchan has been compared to American actress Anne Hathaway. They share similar eyes and smiles, which contribute to their resemblance.\n\n3. **Ranveer Singh and Joaquin Phoenix**:\n   - Indian actor Ranveer Singh has been noted to look similar to American actor Joaquin Phoenix, especially when Ranveer sports a beard.\n\n4. **Priyanka Chopra and Rihanna**:\n   - Actress and former Miss World Priyanka Chopra has been compared to Barbadian singer Rihanna. They share a similar bold and confident demeanor, and some fans have pointed out facial similarities.\n\n5. **Hrithik Roshan and Bradley Cooper**:\n   - Bollywood star Hrithik Roshan is often said to resemble American actor Bradley Cooper. Both have chiseled features and a similar smile.\n\nThese comparisons are often subjective, but they are frequently discussed among fans and in the media.",
